{"tid":217724,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一條女神好感公式","createTime":"2017-04-26T03:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T01:56:21.000Z","uid":108039,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8492018d25dddfb804cb4acc4290efc3a888d7e","tid":217724,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:54:35.000Z","msg":"每個男人起女人心目中都有一個不同嘅好感係數<br />\n好感 = k *n , k 是好感係數, n 是你為女神做了多少件好事<br />\n<br />\n對女人來講, k嘅值如下:<br />\n天撚靚仔 : k = 100<br />\n打扮靚仔 : k = 10<br />\nMK型男 : k = 8<br />\nMK 仔 : k = 5<br />\n毒撚 : k = 0.5<br />\n毒男十字全中: k = - 50<br />\n<br />\n例子:<br />\n如果天然靚仔做一件好事, 女神好感值為: 100*1 = 100<br />\n打扮靚仔做一件好事, 女神好感值為: 10*1 = 10<br />\nMK 型男做一件好事, 女神好感值為: 8*1 = 8<br />\n毒撚做一件好事, 女神好感值為: 0.5* 1 = 0.5<br />\n即係如果打扮靚子 想起女神心目中嘅地位高過天然靚仔, 佢就要為女神做11件好事先得<br />\n如果MK型男想起女神心目中嘅地位高過天然靚仔, 佢就要為女神做13件好事得<br />\n如果毒撚 想打敗MK仔起女神心目中嘅地位, 佢就要 做 5/0.5 = 10 件好事先得<br />\n如果毒男十字全中,你點做都比女神睇唔起, 反而越做越反感<br />\n情況就好似片中13:25 - 14:00嘅片段咁 :"},{"pid":"4c161c2a16d89af2ad0b98197128a378d6ad5f19","tid":217724,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:56:39.000Z","msg":"唔記得比LINK<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pAdW0R3zm7Y?t=13m25s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpAdW0R3zm7Y%3Ft%3D13m25s&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=46a63846\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pAdW0R3zm7Y?t=13m25s</a>"},{"pid":"2a30adef0af1edd9f744a31b27982d97e05d8b86","tid":217724,"uid":5479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"毒撚就乜都不討好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊有0.5"},{"pid":"baac98acb178f7cc1d7f0daf0e4043aba7b18311","tid":217724,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:02:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚就乜都不討好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊有0.5</blockquote><br />\n你中左毒男十字,就會變負數"},{"pid":"fc0d24313dfa42f8abe9e3368a201a8